  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Morse\n\nMorse code is a series of dit(.) and dah(-). Whether something
    is a dit(.) or a dah(-) is dependant on it's length. \n\n1  time unit held =
    dit(.)\n3 time units held = dah(-)\n3 time units of silence = a space (used to
    differentiate letters)\n7 time units of silence = / (used to differentiate words)\n\nThe
    metronome to the right decided how long a time unit is.\n\nAfter 10 time units
    of scilence, the code wil be sent\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
